{"prompt": "Design a corporate website for a waste management service. The design should be pragmatic and utilize a school bus yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Waste Management Services</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #FFDA47; /* School Bus Yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #F5E58A; /* Lighter shade of yellow */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 0.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 1rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-right: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 4rem 2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero h3 {\n            font-size: 2.2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--text-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Reliable Waste Management</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <h3>Your Partner in a Cleaner Tomorrow</h3>\n        <p>We provide comprehensive and eco-friendly waste management solutions for residential and commercial clients. Let us handle your waste responsibly.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Free Quote</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-trash-alt\"></i>\n                <div>\n                    <h3>Residential Waste Collection</h3>\n                    <p>Regular pick-up services for households, including bins and recycling.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-industry\"></i>\n                <div>\n                    <h3>Commercial Waste Management</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored solutions for businesses, from small shops to large industrial sites.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-recycle\"></i>\n                <div>\n                    <h3>Recycling Programs</h3>\n                    <p>Dedicated recycling services to promote sustainability and reduce landfill waste.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-truck-moving\"></i>\n                <div>\n                    <h3>Special Waste Disposal</h3>\n                    <p>Safe and compliant disposal of hazardous or bulky waste items.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Founded on the principles of efficiency and environmental responsibility, our company is dedicated to providing top-tier waste management services. We utilize modern equipment and employ skilled professionals to ensure that your waste is handled with the utmost care and compliance with all regulations. Our commitment is to create cleaner communities and a healthier planet.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>Ready to discuss your waste management needs? Get in touch with us today!</p>\n            <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@wastepro.com</p>\n            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n            <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Waste Management Lane, City, State, ZIP</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Reliable Waste Management. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}